Gary Swanson]] as 1st Detective\n* [[Rockets Redglare]] as Bartender\n* [[Candy Trabucco]] as Accident Bystander\n* [[Nora York]] as Accident Bystander\n* [[Roy Nathanson]] as Accident Bystander\n* [[Michael Emil]] as Abu Bashati\n* [[Emidio LaVella]] as Tomaso\n* [[Christopher Durang]] as Ambulance Attendant\n* [[Danny Devin]] as Sheriff\n* Stanley as Alley Dog\n* Franklin as Abu's Dog\n\n==Further reading==\n* May, Elaine. [https://www.nytimes.com/1990/04/01/movies/film-she-s-a-beginner-but-what-connections.html?scp=9&sq=&pagewanted=all \"FILM: She's a Beginner, but What Connections\"]. ''The New York Times''. (April 1, 1990), p.&nbsp;15, p.&nbsp;24\n* Maslin, Janet. [https://www.nytimes.com/1990/04/06/movies/review-film-a-new-age-comedy-crystals-and-all.html?scp=1&sq=Sandra+Seacat&st=nyt \"Review/Film: A New-Age Comedy, Crystals And All\"]. ''The New York Times''. April 6, 1990.\n* Benson, Sheila. [http://articles.latimes.com/1990-04-11/entertainment/ca-1228_1_spirit-guides \"FILM REVIEW : 'Spirit' Loses Its Comic Flair Halfway Through\"]. ''The Los Angeles Times''. April 11, 1990.\n* Kehr, Dave. [http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1990-08-03/entertainment/9003050262_1_spirit-sandra-seacat-peter-falk \"May And Thomas An Odd Couple In 'Spirit'\"]. ''The Chicago Tribune''. August 3, 1990.\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|0099841}}\n* {{tcmdb title|79152|In the Spirit}}\n* {{rotten-tomatoes|in_the_spirit}}\n* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r5GGOaWFZx4 \"'In the Spirit' Promo\"] on [[YouTube]]\n\n[[Category:1990 films]]\n[[Category:1990s comedy-drama films]]\n[[Category:1990s comedy mystery films]]\n[[Category:American films]]\n[[Category:American black comedy films]]\n[[Category:American comedy-drama films]]\n[[Category:American comedy mystery films]]\n[[Category:1990s black comedy films]]\n[[Category:English-language films]]\n[[Category:Films scored by Patrick Williams]]\n[[Category:Films set in New York (state)]]\n\n{{1990s-comedy-drama-film-stub}}\n", "tex